{"tid":2405456,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱誤扑被告頭  趁法庭小休 警擅閱記事冊","createTime":"2021-02-12T11:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T11:38:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4cddb62a168613d4cbf0c013e811ea689f3cf9f7","tid":2405456,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T11:09:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210212/OLZILHUAQBH5TLKAZ66SCQVH3A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210212%2FOLZILHUAQBH5TLKAZ66SCQVH3A%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FB21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=7d34aa90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210212%2FOLZILHUAQBH5TLKAZ66SCQVH3A%2F&h=8afc876f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210212/OLZILHUAQBH5TLKAZ66SCQVH3A/</a><br />\n<br />\n稱誤扑被告頭 <br />\n趁法庭小休 警擅閱記事冊<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】政府去年2月徵用美孚饒宗頤文化館翠雅山房作武漢肺炎隔離營，遭過千名美孚街坊遊行反對，有人以雜物堵路。三人就在公眾地方造成阻礙及襲警罪受審，其中一名男生被捕時被打至頭破血流，需縫三針。聲稱受襲的警員在庭上供稱與男生糾纏期間被打面，遂拿出警棍打算擊打男生上臂，卻因男生不斷郁動，打中男生前額。這名「扑頭警」作供期間，被踢爆小休時未得法庭許可而擅閱警員記事冊。<br />\n<br />\n警員15399高恩祺（圖）供稱，去年2月2日他便衣當。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n小休期間，李未取得法庭批准，擅自翻閱其警員記事冊，被代表李的大狀質問。高解釋一時大意疏忽，忘記需得到法庭批准才可翻看記事冊。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。押後至本月22日續審。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC1687/20"},{"pid":"b7f3f499b7ed79e78da089d76189de11efeefb9a","tid":2405456,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T11:21:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>高恩祺<br />\n</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a1d6e8a9bdd91d30ac24b0b819661cffbc420df0","tid":2405456,"uid":113000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T11:28:31.000Z","msg":"黑到咁都唔拉妨礙司法公證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef7e52280942e92bab88818eec5cf9e938bebba","tid":2405456,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T11:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=